<td><font color="#00ee00">Misty graveyard</font><font color="#eeeeee">.</font>
</table>
</td></tr></table>
</center>
</font>
<p>
so much better than this?
<p>
<font face="courier, courier new">
<center>
<table bgcolor="black" cellpadding="8" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="60%"><tr><td>
<table
